zoroaster ( or , from greek   zōroastrēs ) , also known as zarathustra ( ;   ( zaraθuštra ) ;   zartosht ,   zardosht ) , or as zarathushtra spitama , was the founder of zoroastrianism .

friedrich nietzsche : " thus spoke " this man , also called zoroaster , the hero of one of nietzsche 's greatest books

